snippet: Antti Raanta, the backup to Henrik Lundqvist, shut out Arizona for all but the final five seconds, and the Rangers won their fifth in a row.
abstract: NHL Roundup; New York Rangers beat Arizona Coyotes, 4-1, in fifth consecutive victory; other hockey scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Antti Raanta, the backup to Henrik Lundqvist, shut out Arizona for all but the final five seconds, and the Rangers won their fifth in a row.

headline.print_headline: Rangers Win Fifth Straight as Raanta Stifles Coyotes
headline.main: Rangers Win Fifth Straight as Raanta Stifles Coyotes
